        "UpdateAsync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，IComputed作为基类接口。Value应该是泛型的TOut对吧？另外异步更新返回什么类型比较合适，Task还是ValueTask？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IComputed",
        "Value",
        "UpdateAsync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Value用TOut泛型。UpdateAsync返回ValueTask<IComputed，这样可以避免异步状态机的分配开销。还有，计算过程中可能出错，需要暴露Error属性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Value",
        "UpdateAsync",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这几个核心成员加上：TOut类型的Value、可空的Exception类型的Error，还有返回ValueTask<IComputed的UpdateAsync方法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IComputed",
        "Value",
        "Error",
        "UpdateAsync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，还缺一个关键机制——当依赖变更时，计算需要被标记为失效。我需要一个Invalidated事件，类型是Action委托，以及一个手动触发失效的Invalidate方法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Invalidated",
        "Invalidate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下细节：Invalidated是event Action类型，Invalidate是无返回值的方法。IsConsistent应该是检查当前值是否仍然有效，返回bool对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Invalidated",
        "Invalidate",
        "IsConsistent"
